<div style="position:absolute;left:214.80px;top:0.54px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ほ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:265.20px;top:0.54px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">もの</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:507.30px;top:0.00px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">課</span><span class="cls_005">:31 (</span><span class="cls_004">頁</span><span class="cls_005">:10/10)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:4.14px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">⑭</span><span class="cls_006">わたしが</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">いちばん</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">欲しい</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_006">物は「どこでも</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">ドア」です。この</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:135.60px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">あ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:267.60px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">い</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:328.80px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ところ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:373.20px;top:20.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">い</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:24.54px" class="cls_006"><span class="cls_006">ドアを  開けると、どこでも   行きたい   所へ  行けます。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:46.80px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">我最想要的東西是</span><span class="cls_013">“</span><span class="cls_002">神奇的門</span><span class="cls_013">”</span><span class="cls_003">，</span><span class="cls_002">打開這扇門</span><span class="cls_003">，</span><span class="cls_002">就可以到任何想去的地方。</span></div>
